money in marketing.

00:05:00.840 --> 00:05:01.920
What we need to have are representative

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:04.000
metrics that our product

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:05.560
or service is better every

00:05:05.560 --> 00:05:07.060
day, for example, conversion

00:05:07.060 --> 00:05:09.040
rates.

00:05:09.900 --> 00:05:10.760
If you, in addition to investing

00:05:10.760 --> 00:05:12.060
in marketing, are attracting

00:05:12.060 --> 00:05:13.820
traffic, etc., what you are

00:05:13.820 --> 00:05:15.360
every day convinces more people,

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:17.440
that is representative

00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:18.200
of that you are doing

00:05:18.200 --> 00:05:18.840
it better.

00:05:19.940 --> 00:05:20.940
These are metrics that are

00:05:20.940 --> 00:05:22.560
more customer-centric.

00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:24.520
And finally, what we learned and

00:05:24.520 --> 00:05:26.600
this is very important is what

00:05:26.600 --> 00:05:28.380
the phases of product development are.

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:31.180
That is, all this we are seeing,

00:05:31.180 --> 00:05:33.100
all this cycle of identifying

00:05:33.100 --> 00:05:34.440
hypotheses, doing experiments,

00:05:34.440 --> 00:05:35.860
building a minimum viable product,

00:05:35.860 --> 00:05:38.080
going learning, going learning if

00:05:38.200 --> 00:05:39.480
we are going well or we are going

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:42.260
wrong and going on or going pivoting,

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:43.680
etc., going building our business

00:05:43.680 --> 00:05:45.000
model, we have to do it in a

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:47.940
series, in an order, in a few

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:50.340
stages that are very clear.

00:05:50.620 --> 00:05:51.680
The first thing we need to do is to

00:05:51.680 --> 00:05:54.520
validate or search for the problem

00:05:54.520 --> 00:05:55.320
solution fit.

00:05:56.040 --> 00:05:57.320
That is, we have to validate that

00:05:57.320 --> 00:05:59.460
this problem really matters something

00:05:59.460 --> 00:06:00.400
to customers.

00:06:00.500 --> 00:06:01.880
By the way, in very many cases

00:06:01.880 --> 00:06:03.840
the projects die here and that

00:06:03.840 --> 00:06:04.820
in addition our solution understands

00:06:04.820 --> 00:06:05.820
and likes.

00:06:06.220 --> 00:06:08.000
And this we have to do, because I don'

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:09.360
t know, the first week, for example,

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:10.420
very quickly, with very

00:06:10.420 --> 00:06:12.060
lean experiments.

00:06:13.100 --> 00:06:14.760
You really have to do it that way.

00:06:15.080 --> 00:06:16.240
If you do not do it and you

00:06:16.240 --> 00:06:18.300
build the product, if you invest

00:06:18.300 --> 00:06:19.680
time and money, without doing

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:21.220
this is a stupid thing, because

00:06:21.220 --> 00:06:22.920
in a very high percentage of

00:06:22.920 --> 00:06:25.060
cases you will realize that

00:06:25.060 --> 00:06:26.840
this problem did not

00:06:26.840 --> 00:06:27.940
exist in the mind of the

00:06:27.940 --> 00:06:29.020
customer, that your solution

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:30.140
is not understood, that your

00:06:30.260 --> 00:06:32.960
solution is not potent, etc.

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:34.500
The higher the degree of innovation,

00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:35.740
the more you have to pay attention

00:06:35.740 --> 00:06:37.000
to this, the more you have to do

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.980
prior experiments.

00:06:38.980 --> 00:06:40.280
The next thing we will look for is

00:06:40.280 --> 00:06:41.340
the product market fit.

00:06:41.420 --> 00:06:42.800
It's that moment when you really

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:45.160
value what you have has

00:06:45.160 --> 00:06:47.920
fit perfectly in a customer

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:49.000
segment.

